page.title: 19Interesting people in Penryn
page.content: {Ken Gill}is one of the intresting people in{Penryn}.He writes all sorts of poems and rhymes about{Penryn.} There was a{V.E}day celebration on and he wrote a poem specialy for it.He has also wrote poems for the{Penryn Junior {School}and one of them has been framed and put on the wall in the hall. {George Folks}is the land lord of{ {"Seven Stars Inn"}he is famous all over the world for his collection of brass.In his Pub he has got coins all over the floor and bar.He has got all sorts of brass objects hanging from the ceiling.
